  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find Sally’s little house,</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a little girl who disappeared in the forest, drawn to something dark that changed her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The path takes you through narrow environments, unsettling corridors, and areas reminiscent of the Backrooms,<br>where sounds, shadows, and presences can catch you by surprise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game focuses on a tense atmosphere, direct jumpscares, and chase moments<br>where getting caught leads to a game over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, survive, and uncover the truth behind Sally’s story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469220/extras/f7b0981fae37916d8debd698dbdf74ed.poster.avif?t=1764846942\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469220/extras/f7b0981fae37916d8debd698dbdf74ed.webm?t=1764846942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469220/extras/f7b0981fae37916d8debd698dbdf74ed.mp4?t=1764846942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>This is my first indie horror game, created to give you a frightening and immersive experience.</u></i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find Sally’s little house,</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a little girl who disappeared in the forest, drawn to something dark that changed her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The path takes you through narrow environments, unsettling corridors, and areas reminiscent of the Backrooms,<br>where sounds, shadows, and presences can catch you by surprise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game focuses on a tense atmosphere, direct jumpscares, and chase moments<br>where getting caught leads to a game over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, survive, and uncover the truth behind Sally’s story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469220/extras/f7b0981fae37916d8debd698dbdf74ed.poster.avif?t=1764846942\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469220/extras/f7b0981fae37916d8debd698dbdf74ed.webm?t=1764846942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469220/extras/f7b0981fae37916d8debd698dbdf74ed.mp4?t=1764846942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>This is my first indie horror game, created to give you a frightening and immersive experience.</u></i></p>",
